ABOUT_US_DOCTOR_SECTION1_P1: Joyina intshukumo yokubonelela ngokuthembakalayo, okunokuhlawulekayo, ukufikelela kwihlabathi jikelele kwimizuzu engama-15 okanye ngaphantsi.
ABOUT_US_DOCTOR_SECTION1_P2: I-MD ye-Saluber yenzelwe ukuguqula ubudlelwane-gulane kunye nesigulane ngokudala u-24/7 ukufikelela kwiinkonzo zezempilo emhlabeni wonke.
about_us_section1_p1: I-SaluberMD iyinkqubo ye-Digital Health eyenzelwe ukuguqula ukuhanjiswa kweenkonzo zonyango kunye nemveliso ukuphucula iziphumo zempilo emhlabeni wonke. Iinkonzo zethu zeDicrosoft Concierge, zinikeza ukufikelela kwiimpilo kunye neempilweni zempilo, ii-odokotela zeebhodi eziqinisekisiweyo, ifayile yezobisi zonyango ngeelwimi ezili-18, iimpahla zokugada ukubeka iliso impilo yakho, kunye nokufikelela kwinethiwekhi yabasebenzi bezempilo kunye neenkonzo.
ABOUT_US_SECTION2_P1:
Ngokusebenzisa i-geo-localization app yethu iya kufumana uGqirha ongcono ngakumbi kuwe. I-SaluberMD Physicians iyakwazi ukuxilonga, ukuphatha, okanye ukuxubusha imeko yakho yezobugqirha ngevidiyo kwaye ikunike isicwangciso socwangciso olufanelekileyo. Uninzi lweemeko eziqhelekileyo eziphathwe kwiofisi yegqirha zinokuphathwa ngotyelelo lwevidiyo.
Ezinye zeemeko esiziphathayo:
ABOUT_US_SECTION2_P2: Ingxelo Yakho Yonyango yindawo efanelekileyo yokugcina yonke idatha yakho yempilo, imifanekiso kunye neefayile. Gcina umkhondo wempilo yakho nge-24/7 ukufikelela kuzo zonke iirekhodi zakho zonyango. Ingaba uhlala ekhaya okanye uhamba ngaphesheya ulwazi lwakho lukhona kwizandla zakho ukuze wabelane ngolwazi lwakho lwezempilo. Ukulula ukusebenzisa iirekhodi zonyango zifumaneka kwiilwimi eziyi-18.
ABOUT_US_SECTION3_P1: Kuphela oogqirha abaqinisekisiweyo bebhodi banikezela ngononophelo lwezempilo kwiSaluberMD. Ezi zengcali ziqinisekiswa, zihlolwe ngokubanzi kwaye ziqeqeshwe ukubonelela ngoncedo oluphezulu. Ugqirha ngamnye unobomi apho unokujonga khona imvelaphi yabo, iziqinisekiso kunye namava. I-SaluberMD izinikezele ekulawuleni uphuculo oluqhubekayo lweeNgcali zethu. Inkqubo yokulinganisela ivumela izigulane ukuba zilinganise oogqirha kwaye zijonge oogqirha jikelele.

PRICING_SECTION1_P1: I-SaluberMD izimisele ukubonelela ngokufanelekileyo, ukunakekelwa kwekhwalithi kwixabiso elingabizi kwaye akukho mali efihlakeleyo okanye iintlawulo.
PRICING_SECTION1_P2: I-SaluberMD inikela ngononophelo naphi na apho nawuyifuna khona ngevidiyo ukutyelela ngodokotela oqinisekisiweyo. Oogqirha bethu bangaxoxa, bahlolisise baze baphulaphule ukuxilonga imiba yenu okanye nje ukujongana nemibuzo yezokwelapha kunye nexhalaba ngelixa ubizwa ngevidiyo.
PRICING_SECTION1_P3: Nge-Medicfile yethu ekhethekileyo unokunika ugqirha wakho ukufikelela kwimbali yakho yonyango, imifanekiso yakho kunye neefayili zokubanceda ukubonelela ngesicwangciso esona sonyango.
QUALITY_INDEX_DESCRIPTION: Ukuqina komzimba yinqanaba lokuqina nokuxinzezeleka kwengqondo ekujongene nokukwazi ukulungelelanisa nokusingatha imeko. Inkcazo yempilo yomzimba ibonakalisa umzimba womntu ukulungelelanisa utshintsho lwendalo kunye nokuvuselela uxinzelelo, ukugcina nokubuyisela amandla okuphila. Ukuqina komzimba kubonakala ngokubonakalayo kubomi babantu, ukufunda, kunye nomsebenzi, kodwa ngokuqhelekileyo nokuzilolonga umzimba. Ubunjani bomzimba bomntu buhlobene nobudlelwane kodwa buhlobene kakhulu nokufumana ukutya okunomsoco kunye nokuzivocavoca umzimba. Ngeendlela ezichanekileyo kunye nokusetyenziswa kakuhle, unokukwazi ukuphucula ukuqina kwakhe emzimbeni kuzo zonke iinkalo.
QUESTIONS_SECTION_TITLE: Thola u-1 ukubonisana ngokukhululekileyo okanye uvavanyo lwezempilo emva kokuzalisa ngokupheleleyo ifayile yakho yezokwelapha.
RECOMMEND_SECTION_P1: KwiSaluberMD silwela ukuhlangabezana neemfuno zokunakekelwa kwempilo kwihlabathi jikelele ngokubonelela abathengi bethu ukuba bafikelele kwiqela elihle le-Physicians.
RECOMMEND_SECTION_P2: Sisoloko sifuna udidi olugqithiseleyo oogqirha ukuba bangeze kwiqela lethu elimangalisayo. Njengelungu leqela lethu siyakuhlonela kwaye sixabise ukuthumela kwakho.
RECOMMEND_SECTION_P3: Nceda ugcwalise ifom apha engezantsi ukuthumela ugqirha kwiSaluberMD

rr_desc: Izinga lokuphefumula lizinga lokuphefumla kwenzeka. Umlinganiselo wokuphefumula oqhelekileyo ekuphumleni komntu omdala ukuphumla kuku-12 ukuya kwe-20 ukuphefumula ngomzuzu. Umlinganiselo wokuphefumula ungaphantsi kwe-12 okanye ngaphezulu kwe-25 iphefumula ngomzuzu xa ukuphumla kuthathwa njengesiqhelo
sai_desc: I-SAI ixhomekeka ngokusesikweni kwintliziyo yakho. Yimitha elula elandelela impendulo yomzimba kwimisebenzi yomzimba - okungaphezulu kwamanyathelo nje. Ngokungafani nokulandelwa kwamanyathelo, i-SCI inikela ngetyala kuyo yonke imisebenzi eyenza intlawulo yenhliziyo: ukubhukuda, ukuhamba ngebhayisikili, ukukhwela, ukudansa, nantoni na. Yigcine ngaphantsi kwe-30 ukuze ube nobomi obubhetele kunye nobomi.
SAVE_MESSAGE: Ukuba uhamba, utshintsho lwakho luya kulahleka
sbpi_desc: Uxinzelelo lwegazi oluphezulu ngumbulali ongenangqondo. Ixabiso legazi le-Systolic neDiastolic liqikelelwa ngexesha leyiphi na iseshoni. Gcina i-SBPI engaphantsi kwe-30 ukuba ube nemingcipheko engaphantsi yokubandezeleka kwiimeko zokusongela ubomi ezifana ne-stroke kunye nama-blood clots.
sci_desc: Ngokuhlalutya ingqungquthela ye-pulse ye-pulse ye-pulse ye-pulse wave (we-pulse wave wave). Inkcazo ye-SCI isishwankathelo sempilo yakho ye-cardiovascular, zama ukuyigcina ngaphantsi kwe-20!

sii_desc: I-SII inxulumene nayo yonke i-indebe yeSaluberMD kwaye isibuko somngcipheko wezempilo jikelele. Ukuba ngaphantsi kwe-30 uhlala kwindawo ephephile!
sl_desc: Inqanaba loxinzelelo libalwe ngokusekelwe kwintsimbi ngomzuzu
spo2_desc: I-SpO2 okanye izinga le-oksijeni yegazi ngumlinganiselo wendlela oksijeni ngayo iiseli ezibomvu zegazi. Iimpawu eziqhelekileyo ziphakathi kwama-95% kunye ne-100%, i-A level below normal-oxygen level ibizwa ngokuba yi-hypoxemia
sri_desc: Sihlalutya iipatheni zokuphefumula ngexesha lesiphi na iseshoni yezokwelapha nangethuba lokulala. Ukuba i-SRI ingaphantsi kwama-30 akho amathuba okuba ahlupheke kwiimeko zokuphefumula eziphazamisayo ziphantsi.
ssi_desc: Ngokuhlalutya ukuhluka kwezinga lentliziyo silinganisa izinga lakho loxinzelelo. Ukuxinezeleka kubonakala kunzima okanye kwandisa umngcipheko weemeko ezifana nokukhuluphala, isifo senhliziyo, isifo se-Alzheimer, isifo sikashukela, ukuxinezeleka, iingxaki zesisu kunye nesifo se-asthma. Gcina ngaphantsi kwe-20 ukuba ube kwindawo ekhuselekileyo!

temperDescription: Imilinganiselo yeemeko ezibandakanya uluhlu lwentetho yesithethi. Iqondo eliphantsi lichaza ukukhathazeka nokukhathazeka. Iqondo eliqhelekileyo lichaza ubudlelwane obunobungane, obufudumele kunye nolwamkelekileyo. Iimpawu eziphakamileyo zomsindo zichaza ukuxhatshazwa, ukulawula kunye neentlungu.

tipshealt1: I-Flu shot - Ngaba kufuneka ndigonywe ngumkhuhlane?
tipshealt10: Cofa apha ukuze uthole olunye ulwazi
tipshealt11: Izibonelelo zonyango zonyango, izidakamizwa ze-cholesterol ezantsi, zigqithise ingozi
tipshealt12: Kwinqaku lokuphonononga kwangoko kwiseLancet, abaphandi baphetha ukuba iinzuzo zokunciphisa i-cholesterol ye-LDL kunye neyeza-statin ziyakuthintela iziganeko ezinkulu (izifo zentliziyo, izibetho) kwaye zigqithise ingozi yeziyobisi.
tipshealt13: Ngokutsho kwabaphandi iziganeko ezimbi kakhulu eziye zaboniswa ukuba zibangelwa yonyango lexesha elide liyi-myopathy (ichazwa njengentlungu yesifo okanye ubuthakathaka), isifo seswekile esitsha, kwaye, mhlawumbi, isifo esiyingozi.
tipshealt2: Nangona umgudu wokugonya umkhuhlane awusoloko unika ukukhuselwa ngokupheleleyo, kuyafaneleka ukufumana. I-CDC (iZiko loLawulo lweZifo kunye nokuPhepha) lincoma iigciwane zentsholongwane zonyaka ngamnye umntu oneminyaka eyi-6 okanye ngaphezulu. Ukugonywa kubaluleke kakhulu kubantu abasemngciphekweni omkhulu weengxaki ze-influenza, kubandakanywa
tipshealt5: Abantwana abaselula (ngaphantsi kweminyaka engama-4 nangaphezulu kweenyanga ezintandathu)
tipshealt6: Umsebenzi wokwenyama uphucula imemori nezakhono zokucinga
tipshealt7: Ukusebenza rhoqo ngokomzimba kunokuphucula ukusebenza kwengqondo kwixesha lokuphila nokunciphisa ingozi yokugula komzimba.
tipshealt8: Izifundo ezininzi ziye zashicilelwa ekusebenzisaneni okufutshane kunye nenzuzo yokusebenza rhoqo ngokomzimba kunye nokuphuculwa komsebenzi wokuqonda.
tipshealt9: Iimpembelelo ngqo ngqo kwingqondo nangendlela engathanga ngokusetyenziswa kwamanyathelo kunye nomzimba emzimbeni.

valenceDescription: Utshintsho olususela ekungabikho kokungabikho komsebenzi. Xa uphulaphule umntu uthetha, kunokwenzeka ukuba aqonde indlela "efanelekileyo" okanye "engalunganga" abavakalelwa ngayo ngento, into okanye isiganeko esicatshulweyo.
va_desc: I-Vascular Age inikezela umlinganiselo wexesha elibonakalayo leemibhobho zakho, xa kuthelekiswa nabantu abaphilileyo. Ukuba ubudala bakho be-vascular bukhulu kunexesha lakho lexesha, ungase ube mngciphekweni wokuba nesifo sengqondo (CVD) kamva ebomini.

VIDEOCALL_DES2: Xa ufumana ifowuni, nqakraza kwixande eliya kubonakala liza kuthatha umnxeba.
